Introduction

Kim TaeHyung, popularly known as J.Seph, is the main rapper and lead dancer of the group KARD under DSP Media. He represents the letter A and the Ace card. J.Seph, the Ace, explained: “The Ace can either be the lowest card that supports the team or the highest card that is sharp.”

J.Seph debuted as a member of KARD on July 19, 2017, with the mini album Hola Hola.

He enlisted for his mandatory military service as an active duty soldier on October 5, 2020, and was eventually discharged on April 4th, 2022.
